Hello, thank you for calling Harmony Music School. My name is Alan Adams. May I have your name, please?

Hi Alan, my name is Nicole Campbell.

Thank you, Nicole. How can I assist you today?

I’m really anxious because I need to return a music book I purchased last week, and I’m not sure about your return process.

I understand, Nicole. No need to worry, I’m here to help. Can I first have your order number, please?

Sure, the order number is one two three four five.

Thank you. I also need your email address to proceed with the return process.

It’s nicole.campbell@example.com.

Great, Nicole! I’ve processed your return request. You’ll receive a confirmation email shortly. Is there anything else I can assist you with?

No, that’s all. Thank you, Alan!

You're welcome, Nicole. Thank you for your time, and have a great day!
